PÅTIENT BLOCKS OUT MEMORIES

28:24.840 --> 28:27.800
ACCIDENT DEATH DAUGHTER
DISASSOCIATED

28:28.000 --> 28:30.280
UNDER INFLUENCE
THOMAS SPECTRE

28:36.760 --> 28:41.600
Hi, Benoit, this is Veronique.
Can you call me back, please? Bye.

29:00.800 --> 29:03.120
Hi. Veronique.
- Hi.

29:03.320 --> 29:05.040
How are you?

29:06.160 --> 29:07.280
Are you still cross?

29:07.480 --> 29:11.560
No, it's a long time ago. But
you could've invited me to your wedding.

29:11.760 --> 29:14.520
I thought you may've still been hurt
at the time and...

29:14.720 --> 29:17.480
How are you?
- I've got a little girl now.

29:17.680 --> 29:20.320
Are you happy?
- Yes.

29:20.520 --> 29:25.640
Well, our Romy isn't an easy child
and Mie finds it hard to cope.

29:25.840 --> 29:27.360
She's got depression.

29:27.800 --> 29:29.400
I miss you.

30:03.720 --> 30:08.120
LAST FEBRUARY

30:09.280 --> 30:13.520
My mother-in-law saw us.
I need to make a decision. I have to...

30:13.720 --> 30:15.000
I have to choose.

30:16.080 --> 30:17.720
Choose us, Benoit.

30:27.200 --> 30:28.320
Hi.

30:28.800 --> 30:30.320
Veronique...

30:31.120 --> 30:32.640
Sorry, but I'm not coming.

30:32.840 --> 30:37.040
What do you mean, you're not coming?
- That... I'm not coming.

30:38.360 --> 30:41.760
Benoit, we arranged to meet
to decide what we would do.

30:41.960 --> 30:47.040
Veronique, Mie took an overdose of
sleeping pills yesterday.

30:49.000 --> 30:54.560
This... We can't see each other anymore.
We can't. I have to choose my family.

30:54.760 --> 30:56.280
Sorry.

31:12.000 --> 31:15.160
He's left me for that bitch again.

31:15.360 --> 31:17.320
Mie has taken my life away from me.

31:17.520 --> 31:21.360
I should've been on that stage and not
in the fucking courtroom like my father.

31:21.560 --> 31:24.760
I should wake up
next to Benoit every morning.

31:26.040 --> 31:28.320
Why didn't she take enough pills?

31:29.480 --> 31:31.120
Benoit is mine.

31:31.760 --> 31:33.160
Mine.

31:33.360 --> 31:35.880
He is the only one
I have ever really loved.

31:36.080 --> 31:39.280
Apart from Daniël, your little brother?
- He has nothing to do with it.

31:39.480 --> 31:41.080
Daniël is dead, Benoit is alive.

31:41.280 --> 31:44.480
Your happiness shouldn't depend on others.

31:44.680 --> 31:48.520
We are all the architects of
our own happiness.

31:50.560 --> 31:52.800
We have to take control of it ourselves.

