REHEARSALS 7 - 8 P.M.

33:21.360 --> 33:22.920
Is anyone sitting here?

33:25.400 --> 33:29.120
Is anyone waiting for you at home?
- My cat.

33:32.120 --> 33:35.320
You've got beautiful eyes.

33:37.280 --> 33:40.400
Did you come by car?
- By car.

34:12.840 --> 34:14.640
